---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DiagnoseTool from '../components/DiagnoseTool';
---

<Layout title="問題診斷" description="使用互動式工具快速診斷 SD 卡問題，獲得專業的解決方案推薦">
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">SD 卡問題診斷工具</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          回答幾個簡單問題，我們會為你分析問題並推薦最適合的解決方案
        </p>
      </div>

      <DiagnoseTool client:load />

      <div class="mt-16 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">診斷工具如何運作？</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🎯</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">精準分析</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">根據你的回答，判斷問題類型和嚴重程度</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">📊</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">成功率預估</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">基於數千個案例，提供救援成功率參考</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🛠️</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">工具推薦</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">推薦最適合的免費或付費救援工具</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
